      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙下。【第十一场：佳期】",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00072",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "红娘、崔莺莺同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00073",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "崔莺莺"
      ],
      "text": "那夜晚似不该绝人太甚，效私奔羞得我小鹿撞心。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00074",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐别害羞，男大当婚女大当嫁，谁也免不了这回事的，待我叫他开门来。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00075",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，妙啊！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00076",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00077",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "听叫门想必是小姐来临，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00078",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "小姐来了，请啊！哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00079",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "请小姐莫负这良辰美景。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00080",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "啊，红娘姐，外面有人来了，请你与我看上一看。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00081",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "红娘出，张珙关门。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00082",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "张相公，张相公！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00083",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "红娘姐，这时候我也顾不得你了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00084",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙拉崔莺莺同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00085",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "张相公，张相公！他们也顾不得我了，想他们双双同入罗帏，竟将我红娘关在门外。张相公，啊张……红娘啊红娘，你这算何苦啊！",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00086",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反四平调",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐小姐多风采，君瑞君瑞你大雅才。风流不用千金买，月移花影玉人来。今宵勾却了相思债，无限的春风抱满怀。花心拆，游蜂采，柳腰摆，露滴牡丹开。一个是半推半就惊又爱，好一似襄王神女赴阳台。不管我红娘在门儿外，这冷露湿透了我的凤头鞋。",
      "text_length": 113
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00087",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "什么我的鞋儿也湿啦，张相公，张相公，你的相思病好了九成了吧！",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00088",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "琴童上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00089",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童"
      ],
      "text": "我的一成汗还没有出哪！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00090",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "红娘逃下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00091",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童"
      ],
      "text": "好啊！你们做的好事，我去问红娘借钱，她要是不答应，我就告诉欢郎，让老夫人知道也好晓得我的厉害！",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000004_e00092",
      "play_id": "90000004",
      "scene_id": "90000004_s01",
